Class Summary 
Class Description
Billing
This class contains the methods used to filter, display, and rent a room in the hotel.
CSVManager
This class contains methods used to export and import CSV files containing informations on the rooms.
Main
This class launches the program.
Menu
This class contain the navigation menu.
Room
This class represents a room and it's informations : Room number, Category, Capacity, Price and it's availability.
RoomCategory
This class represents a room category and it's informations : the category ID and it's description.
